{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_63022.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm05_event08","chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"Are those Mongolian soldiers...over there?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":833300}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"...Is someone being chased?"},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"From what I saw, there are only a few@Mongolian soldiers."},{"chara":[{"id":105101}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"I spotted a suspicious group during patrol@and decided to follow them..."},{"chara":[{"id":105101}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"They're probably over there."},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"...Deki, please inform the Lama about this.@I will..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833900,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Deki","textRight":"Heruka, what are you going to do?!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":400,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"...save the townspeople!@There are Tibetans being attacked over there."},{"chara":[{"id":105101}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"I'm going to go and meet them, so..."},{"chara":[{"id":105101}],"nameCenter":"Heruka","textCenter":"Please come with me, everyone."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":105101,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833900,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Deki","textRight":"[chara:833900:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!"},{"nameNarration":"Citizens","narration":"\"C-coming with you...\"","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"\"We might get hurt...\""},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"You don't need to worry."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":105101,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"If you follow me, everything will surely be fine."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"...She always tries to be special like this..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"Reluctantly, the townspeople cooperated.","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"Then, the Mongolian soldiers realized@that it was futile to attack when they saw@the townspeople gathering, so they fled."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":300}],"narration":"...Well, it was just a bluff.@It worked because they were outnumbered.@Nothing too surprising."},{"narration":"Rather...what was truly astonishing was that@the group we helped were the survivors from@the northern nunnery, which had been attacked@by the Mongolian Army."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_63022.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":833900}],"nameLeft":"Northern Nunnery Junior Nun","textLeft":"I'm sorry for dragging you into this...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"nameRight":"Northern Nunnery Junior Nun","textRight":"But we have nowhere else to go..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"It's not like we're going to kick you out.@That would be pointless."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":105101,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"Why don't we all get along here...? Right?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":105101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_63022.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Northern Nunnery Junior Nun","textLeft":"...Right. Hey, do you think that girl might be..."},{"chara":[{"id":833900}],"nameRight":"Northern Nunnery Junior Nun","textRight":"I'm sure of it. It must be her..."},{"nameNarration":"Northern Nunnery Junior Nuns","narration":"\"The Rakshasi of this nunnery!\"","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"narrationEffect":"out","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"Huh..."},{"chara":[{"id":833300,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"...Tsk."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":105101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Northern Nunnery Junior Nun","textLeft":"If the Rakshasi is here, we're safe."},{"chara":[{"id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"nameRight":"Northern Nunnery Junior Nun","textRight":"Let's defeat the Mongolian Army together!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"No, I..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Dolma","textLeft":"Heruka is tired right now, so let's talk@about this later."},{"chara":[{"id":833300}],"nameLeft":"Dolma","textLeft":"...And you guys, don't you have@something to report?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","pos":2}],"nameRight":"Northern Nunnery Junior Nun","textRight":"Oh, yes..."},{"chara":[{"id":833300,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Dolma","textLeft":"Anyway, let's go to the nunnery."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"Heruka","narration":"Then...the junior nuns from the northern@nunnery told their story to the Lama,@describing what they had experienced.","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"It seems that there was a Rakshasi@at the northern nunnery, but..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp3.json","id":105101}],"narration":"Their precious friends...the respected Lama@from the north...it seemed that these people@had fallen victim to the Mongolian soldiers@and were possessed by \"demons.\""},{"narration":"I didn't fully understand the details,@but in any case, they were defeated."},{"narration":"Anyway, all the other nunneries except for@this one seemed to have fallen into the hands@of the Mongolian Army."},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":300}],"narration":"This place was their last hope..."},{"narration":"But the Lama's decision was unexpected@and disappointed everyone."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":105101}],"narration":"...Except for me."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_63013.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833800,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story08","chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameCenter":"Lama","textCenter":"I apologize for gathering you all at this late hour.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameCenter":"Lama","textCenter":"However, there is something urgent@I need to tell you..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833800}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"...Dolma, are you alright even though@it's nighttime?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833300}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"I'm fine because you're here, Heruka."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":105101},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833300}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833800,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Lama","textCenter":"The northern nunnery has been razed to@the ground by the Mongolian Army."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameCenter":"Lama","textCenter":"It seems the northern Rakshasi put up a fight,@but unfortunately..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833800}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameCenter":"Junior Nuns","textCenter":"No way..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":833800,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Lama","textCenter":"Currently, there is no other nunnery@we can contact."},{"chara":[{"id":833800}],"nameCenter":"Lama","textCenter":"We are isolated and there is no hope of rescue,@so we have no other choice."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":833800,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Lama","textCenter":"We will abandon this nunnery and begin@preparations for evacuation."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833800}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0","motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1","motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameCenter":"Junior Nuns","textCenter":"...?!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_0"},{"effect":"fadeout","id":833900,"live2dName":"live2d_1"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":833800,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Lama","textCenter":"Naturally, no Rakshasi rituals will be performed."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":833800}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":833300,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"Why...?@Hey, Heruka...why?"},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"Why...?@Well, there's no helping it, right? Besides..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":105101}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"...Isn't it okay already?@Don't dream of becoming a Rakshasi anymore."},{"chara":[{"id":105101}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"Let's all escape together and live happily@in some village..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":833300,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"...He...hehe. I...I see..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":105101,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"What's wrong?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":833300,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"Just watch, Heruka.@I'll change things for you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":833300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textRight":"I will save you!"},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"What do you mean...by that..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":833300,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textBg":"shout","textRight":"Everyone!"},{"chara":[{"id":833300}],"nameRight":"Dolma","textBg":"shout","textRight":"Capture the Lama!@He's an ally of the Mongols!"},{"chara":[{"id":105101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Heruka","textLeft":"...?!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}